Garrity Says Meg Whitman as HP CEO Is `Crazy Idea'

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-21T21:20:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/garrity-says-meg-whitman-as-hp-ceo-is-crazy-idea-video.html
David Garrity, principal at GVA 
Research LLC, talks about challenges facing Hewlett-Packard Co. 
and potential replacements for Chief Executive Officer Leo 
Apotheker.  Hewlett-Packard, facing investor frustration over 
sales-forecast cuts and jarring strategy shifts, is considering 
replacing Apotheker, two people familiar with the matter said. 
Garrity speaks with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson on Bloomberg 
Television's "Street Smart." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 03:23
 